  "page": null,
  "source": "[\\axiom.of.empty.set]\nAxiom: \"Axiom of Empty Set\"\nthen:\n. exists: E is \\set\n  suchThat:\n  . forAll: x is \\set\n    then:\n    . not: x \"in\" E\nDocumented:\n. description: \"There exists a set $\\emptyset$ such that for every set $x$, $x \\notin \\emptyset$. This set is a reasonable starting point from which further sets are built.\"\nId: \"eeec7d4c-0615-4a7b-a0d0-d110c8a6f033\"",
